{"word":"ἐμπίνω","slug":"ἐμπίνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐμπίνω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-πίομαι</el>) (aor2 <el>ἐνέπιον</el>) (<a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <el>ἐμπέπτωκα</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἐν'><el>ἐν</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to drink in, drink greedily</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>ἐμπ. τοῦ αἵματος</el> <i>to drink greedily of</i> the blood, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to drink one's fill</i>, <b><a href='S:Theognis'>Theogn.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}